394
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:20,720
Why not ask

395
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:22,480
your benefactor for another favor?

396
00:28:23,830 --> 00:28:25,350
What more can he ask?

397
00:28:25,790 --> 00:28:27,170
I heard plenty of people wait

398
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:28,750
