468
00:30:47,360 --> 00:30:48,520
Get out at the next junction;

469
00:30:48,520 --> 00:30:49,620
Li Long will ride with me.

470
00:30:49,620 --> 00:30:50,950
You take your team to the plant.

471
00:30:50,960 --> 00:30:52,230
Find Jiao Yu no matter what.

472
00:30:53,750 --> 00:30:54,850
As expected, he didn't plan

473
00:30:54,850 --> 00:30:55,980
